@brigadas
title: Las brigadas campesinas
subtitle: [? if via = "armada" or via = "dual" : The PDLP's brigades and your columns work the Costa Grande as one structure. ?][? if via = "politica" or via = "institucional" : The brigades' villages opened to your organizers — the sierra's credit spent on your work. ?]
